Puma Clyde All-Pro Elf (GS)
results.story: Offered in grade school sizing, the Elf x PUMA Clyde All-Pro Jr ‘Buddy the Elf’ celebrates the 2003 Christmas-themed comedy film starring Will Ferrell. The performance hoops shoe takes inspiration from the titular character, featuring a mostly green engineered woven upper lined in candy cane-striped textile. Buddy’s gold-buckle belt adorns the tongue, while the heel tab of the left shoe is accessorized with the character’s pointed cap. A graphic depicting his syrupy spaghetti dish decorates the opposite shoe.
